f=AI & Agents/anneal/operational/skill/anneal-skill-routing.md · h1:anneal Skill Routing (no identity layer non-leader)=`lesson/post-mortem/diagnosis ─► self-annealing-loop (locate + draft + baseline) \· └► skill-lifecycle (propose → board → apply → version) \· audit cadence ─► skill-quality-audit ─findings─► skill-lifecycle (fixes) / meta (structure) / false-positive log \· thinking-pattern failure ─► prompt-context-engineering ─► (same proposal path, Shared OS copy) \· every applied change ─► gauge (re-measure; closure evidence)` · h1:anneal Skill Routing (no identity layer non-leader)=Handoffs out: board meta's fleet-governance (every edit) precedent (archives) meta (gap findings, structural issues) gauge (closure) forge ("skill issue" diagnoses arrive there). Precedence: annealing-loop coordinates; lifecycle executes; audit finds. board dormant everything queues, nothing auto-applies (warning labels only, skill-lifecycle Fallback).